  "remarks": "QDe.151. Emerged on 13 Sep. 2014. Most known for its abduction and subsequent beheading of French national Herve Gourdel. Claimed responsibility for attacking police and gendarmes in Algeria and continued planning future attacks. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020.; Listing: Listed by the 1267 Committee on 29 Sep. 2015 ( amended on 24 Nov. 2020 )",
